As far as who gts what buffs cast on them , this like everything else is determined by the raid leader or whomever they desigante to decide such things. The raid leaders instructions and decisions are law and should not be disputed at the time of the raid. As far as what classes get symbol cast on them at raids run by Azure, I can't anser that as I am a druid and have nothing to do with it. Perhaps Azure can give some insight on this issue.<br>
<br>
The point is that the raid fee pays for more things than just buffs. What all I couldnt tell you. Im not the raid leader. I would like to point out that Azure has reduced the raid fee from 50pp to 30pp as far less was being spent then that being taken in so the fee was reduced. again, azure would be the best one to ask who gets symbol cast on them . <p>Falcone Robinsbane<BR>
